Edit a list of pages in a single operation by applying a regular expression 
to each page's content.

See http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:MassEditRegex for full instructions.

Briefly:

  1. Add to LocalSettings.php:

    include_once("$IP/extensions/MassEditRegex/MassEditRegex.php");

  2. Go to [[Special:MassEditRegex]]

  3. If you don't have access, go to [[Special:User rights management]] and add yourself to the Bot group.
